# Code Language Standards

## English-Only Code Policy

All code blocks generated during Cursor agent interactions must strictly adhere to English-only standards.

### Requirements

**Comments and Documentation**
- All comments must be written in English only
- Function/method documentation strings in English
- Variable and function names in English
- No non-English characters in code
